    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">The ASR Tactical Kevlar Cord is ideal for your survival kit. Made from 3 strands of Kevlar thread, it has a breaking strength of 200 lbs. This cord is coated in polyurethane, which gives it added abrasion and UV resistance. Weighing less than a few ounces, the Kevlar survival cord is optimal for traps, bows, snares and more. This cord is a perfect addition to any emergency kit. Buy in bulk lengths for additional savings.</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Cord Made with Kevlar Survival Paracord Rope 200lbs Strength (Various Lengths)</h2>\n  <p>The ASR Tactical Kevlar Cord is ideal for your survival kit. Made from 3 strands of Kevlar thread, it has a breaking strength of 200 lbs. This cord is coated in polyurethane, which gives it added abrasion and UV resistance.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>HIGH YIELD STRENGTH - Possesses a tensile strength of 200 lbs.</li>\n    <li>CUT RESISTANT - Kevlar cord is highly resistant to cutting, friction, and high temperatures</li>\n    <li>BRAIDED DESIGN - Braided polyester sleeving adds extra durability and helps to prevent unraveling</li>\n    <li>MULTIPURPOSE USE - High yield strength, cut resistant core, heat resistance, and braided exterior make this an ideal product for sports, camping, and survival application</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS - Length:</strong> 25 Feet, Diameter: 1 mm, Weight: 0.2 lbs., Color: Yellow or Blue</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1600x1600/camping_outdoors/cord/ksc_kevlar_tacwrap_newparent.png\" alt=\"The ASR Tactical Kevlar Cord is ideal for your survival kit\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> ASRKEV013-408</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 766359858104</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>Weighing less than a few ounces, the Kevlar survival cord is optimal for traps, bows, snares and more.</p>\n  <p>This cord is a perfect addition to any emergency kit. Buy in bulk lengths for additional savings.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
